 fait briller le jour.","en":"And He darkened its night and extracted its brightness.","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"وَأَغْطَشَ","fr":"Et Il darkened","en":"And He darkened","tr":"wa-aghṭasha","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"لَيْلَهَا","fr":"son nuit","en":"its night","tr":"laylahā","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"وَأَخْرَجَ","fr":"et apporta hors","en":"and brought out","tr":"wa-akhraja","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"ضُحَىٰهَا","fr":"son éclat","en":"its brightness","tr":"ḍuḥāhā","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":30,"verseKey":"79:30","juz":30,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضَ بَعْدَ ذَٰلِكَ دَحَىٰهَآ","fr":"La terre, après cela, Il l’a nivelée.","en":"And after that He spread the earth.","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"وَٱلْأَرْضَ","fr":"Et la terre","en":"And the earth","tr":"wal-arḍa","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"بَعْدَ","fr":"après","en":"after","tr":"baʿda","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"ذَٰلِكَ","fr":"que","en":"that","tr":"dhālika","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"دَحَىٰهَآ","fr":"Il répandu cela","en":"He spread it","tr":"daḥāhā","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":31,"verseKey":"79:31","juz":30,"arabic":"أَخْرَجَ مِنْهَا مَآءَهَا وَمَرْعَىٰهَا","fr":"Il en a fait sortir eaux et pâturages.","en":"He extracted from it its water and its pasture,","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"أَخْرَجَ","fr":"Il apporta en avant","en":"He brought forth","tr":"akhraja","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"مِنْهَا","fr":"de cela","en":"from it","tr":"min'hā","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"مَآءَهَا","fr":"son eau","en":"its water","tr":"māahā","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"وَمَرْعَىٰهَا","fr":"et son pâturage","en":"and its pasture","tr":"wamarʿāhā","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":32,"verseKey":"79:32","juz":30,"arabic":"وَٱلْجِبَالَ أَرْسَىٰهَا","fr":"Les montagnes, Il les a implantées,","en":"And the mountains He set firmly","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"وَٱلْجِبَالَ","fr":"Et les montagnes","en":"And the mountains","tr":"wal-jibāla","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"أَرْسَى